## Inherited Governance (Sutra D27/D28)
Every Write/Edit must emit (a) an Input Routing block (`INPUT/TYPE/ROUTE/FIT CHECK/ACTION`) and (b) a Depth block (`TASK/DEPTH/EFFORT/COST/IMPACT`). Markers are per-turn — they expire on every new founder prompt. Any edit touching `os/**` or Sutra-owned files runs at Depth 5. Hard enforcement is live via `.claude/hooks/sutra/` — the dispatcher blocks on missing markers.

